    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 25. Darwinoplectanum figueiredoi n. gen. n. sp. 17. Holotype whole-mount (ventral). 18 – 19. Copulatory complex. 20. Squamodisc. 21. Ventral bar (bent at mid-lenght). 22. Sinistral dorsal bar. 23. Hook. 24. Ventral anchor. 25. Dorsal anchor. Fig. 17 scale of 100 μm; Figs. 18 – 19 scale of 10 μm; Figs. 20 – 25 scale of 25 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/206734/files/figure.png" ;
